OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLengthy sunny spells between
OL,6,Fpatchy amounts of cloud. Most places
OL,7,Fwill remain dry, but the odd light
OL,8,Fpassing shower is possible at first.
OL,9,FFresh westerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and bright evening with
OL,12,Fsome hazy sunny spells. The rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will remain dry with clear
OL,14,Fspells. Gentle to moderate westerly
OL,15,Fwinds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA dry and bright day with
OL,18,Fsome sunshine, albeit often rather
OL,19,Fhazy. Mainly gentle winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
